::Kaiser::
       He rolls under DeathSteel's flip and comes up to his feet facing his 
opponent.  "Come now DeathSteel, you'll have to do better than that."  He 
thinks for a moment.  "You may have two more passes before I begin my attack. 
 I recommend that you don't underestimate me again."  He adopts another 
defensive stance and lowers his center of gravity for the next approach."

--part1_1e8.5248906.2bb26f9d_boundary
